node.text:
🥁Turn Up The Base Powder Foundation is literal perfection when it comes to formula. It’s Buildable and Blurringans it wears beautifully with the Secure The Blur Primer underneath! On my model @rsjdesign this pair is the ultimate dream for his flawless natural looking base. The powder evened out his skin tone and cover some pimples. Last, I finished the look with a the Clear Brow Kiki Brow Gel. Tag a friend that could use this! SHOP it out NOW @sephora and @onesize // If you need help finding your shade send @onesizeshadefinder so we can help you find your shade! 
.
❤️Thank you @rsjdesign @rsjcollection for being my model! #onesizebeauty #turnupthebase

node.title: 🔥This POWDER FOUNDATION is THE BEST for MEN!

node.text:
This powder foundation is a game changer! It’s the rice silk powder that makes this powder different than any other! It literally BLURS the skin on my friend @noataieb 🙌🏽 Its medium to full coverage and in the video, you can see how I was able to build the coverage under his eyes and on his entire face. It has an amazing soft matte (not flat) finish and this powder comes in 32 shades with a variety of undertones! Tag a friend who needs to see this tutorial!
🥁Check it out now in Sephora and OneSizeBeauty.com // $33 USD $41 CAD #onesizebeauty #turnupthebase

node.title: NATURAL MAKEUP FOR MEN! Using the @onesize Powder Foundation!

node.text:
This natural makeup look anyone can do with a little ‘Secure The Blur’ Primer and the @onesize ‘Turn Up the Base Versatile Powder Foundation’!! It’s buildable, blendable, bulletproof, buttery and BLURRING! If you haven’t tried it- def check it out at a Sephora near you! Also if you have issues finding your shade- send a DM to @onesizeshadefinder so we can match you! Anyone can wear this because Makeup is a @onesize fits all!
#turnupthebase #onesizebeauty

node.title: NATURAL Makeup with NO liquid foundation or concealer!

node.text:
After being hospitalized for my respiratory issues, my parents immediately flew to LA. Being headstrong and independent, I didn’t want to be a bother to them. Little did I know, this is exactly what I needed. I would do everything and anything for them and it’s all I know growing up Filipino. Love is in our blood. 🇵🇭 (That’s why my brand @onesize is red and pink) My mom and dad wearing my costumes will be a memory in my mind and heart forever… because in this “closet” they said they were proud of me. 🥺❤️
.
🥁Also, they’re wearing my costumes from my biggest complexion launch campaigns- Turn Up the Base Powder Foundation & Turn Up the Base Butter Silk Concealer. (And I’m wearing the Brow Kiki Jacket) So cool to see my biggest supporters wearing these items that are part of monumental moments in my life and professional career. Like these costumes- they’re one of a kind. 
.
Thank you @mamastarrr @papastarrr I love you so much ❤️❤️❤️ #mahalkita

node.text:
🥁Turn Up The Base Powder Foundation is literal perfection when it comes to formula. It’s Buildable and Blurringans it wears beautifully with the Secure The Blur Primer underneath! On my model @rsjdesign this pair is the ultimate dream for his flawless natural looking base. The powder evened out his skin tone and cover some pimples. Last, I finished the look with a the Clear Brow Kiki Brow Gel. Tag a friend that could use this! SHOP it out NOW @sephora and @onesize // If you need help finding your shade send @onesizeshadefinder so we can help you find your shade! 
.
❤️Thank you @rsjdesign @rsjcollection for being my model! #onesizebeauty #turnupthebase
